OL,3,CInquest opened into fundraiser and
OL,4,Crecord-breaker Claire Lomas' death
OL,6,FAn inquest has been opened into the
OL,7,Fdeath of disability campaigner Claire
OL,8,FLomas.
OL,10,FClaire Lomas, from Leicestershire,
OL,11,Fdied following an accident in Amman,
OL,12,Fcapital of Jordan, on 22 August aged
OL,13,F44.
OL,15,FThis was opened by Assistant Coroner
OL,16,FMiss Thistlethwaite and has been
OL,17,Fadjourned to 25th November 2024.
OL,19,FSince she was paralysed in a riding
OL,20,Faccident in 2007 Ms Lomas committed
OL,21,Fher life to raising money for charity.
