OL,3,CInquest opened into fundraiser and
OL,4,Crecord-breaker Claire Lomas' death
OL,6,FOver 14 years she raised almost #1
OL,7,Fmillion. She famously walked the
OL,8,FLondon Marathon marathon in 2012
OL,9,Fwearing a "bionic suit" and completed
OL,10,Fthe Great North Run in Newcastle last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FShe was awarded an MBE for her
OL,14,Ffundraising in 2017.
